<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c3">{فَمَا لَهُمْ عَنِ التَّذْكِرَةِ مُعْرِضِينَ , كَأَنَّهُمْ حُمُرٌ مُسْتَنْفِرَةٌ , فَرَّتْ مِنْ قَسْوَرَةٍ}</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص١٦١:</span> <span class="c3">{مُسْتَنْفِرَةٌ}</span>: نَافِرَةٌ , مَذْعُورَةٌ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c3">{قَسْوَرَةٌ}</span>: رِكْزُ النَّاسِ وَأَصْوَاتُهُمْ، وَكُلُّ شَدِيدٍ قَسْوَرَةٌ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ أَبُو هُرَيْرَةَ:</span> القَسْوَرَةُ: قَسْوَرُ الأَسَدُ،<span class="c5"> الرِّكْزُ:</span> الصَّوْتُ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) [المدثر: ٤٩ - ٥١]</p> </div>